<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.6">
<l>umpa rulakō ṭuyirellā muntiyil</l>
<l>vampu malarmēl paṭaittāṉai māyōṉai</l>
<l>ampaṉṉa kaṇṇā ḷacōtaitaṉ ciṅkattai</l>
<l>nampaṉai nāṭi naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having searched for god, the one who created</l>
<l>The heavens, earth, [and] all living creatures</l>
<l>On a fragrant flower in [his] navel, Māyōṉ,</l>
<l>The lion of Yaśodā, the [lady] with arrow-like eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw [him] in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
